review_data: Reviewed in the United States on June 7, 2021
name: Richard A. Klein
title: Ice Cream-like yogurt
review: This is my favorite yogurt. It almost tastes like ice cream compared to other brands and flavors. Not too sweet, less fermented taste than most! I like also the higher protein. Their Strawberry is not too bad too but this has become my only yogurt that I will eat, lately.

review_data: Reviewed in the United States on February 15, 2021
name: Captain Awesomeness
title: My favorite of all the Icelandic Provisions
review: I'm fairly certain I've had every single possibility by this brand as I'm such a sucker for Whole Foods price drops.This is my favorite in part because of taste but in so many ways due to texture of the variety of agreements. With added whipped cream this is a spectacular treat. My "go-to" of the Icelandic Skyr, to the point even when not on sale I tend to order at least one of this flavor (but none of the other ones, for they aren't worthy).

title: Love this yogert!
review: I love yogert, and i have had them all i think. This is my favorite brand. The right amount of sweet and just enough fruit and tiny nuts.The texture is perfect.The store only lets me buy 5 at a time, so i guess everyone loves it too.
